<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.3.9">
<l>tiṇṇārveṇ caṅkuṭai yāytiru nāḷtiru vōṇamiṉ ṟēḻu nāḷ muṉ</l>
<l>paṇṇēr moḻiyāraik kūvi muḷaiyaṭṭip pallāṇṭu kūṟu vittēṉ</l>
<l>kaṇṇālam ceyyak kaṟiyum kalatta tariciyu mākki vaittēṉ</l>
<l>kaṇṇānī nāḷaittoṭ ṭukkaṉṟiṉ piṉpōkēl</l>
<l>kōlañcey tiṅkē yiru.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Bearer of the powerful white conch,</l>
<l rend="indent">7 days from now is the holy day of Ōṇam.</l>
<l>Having summoned those with melodious speech and planted the sprouts,</l>
<l rend="indent">I caused “many years’ to be intoned.</l>
<l>I made curry and rice for the festival and put [them] in pots.</l>
<l>Kaṇṇaṉ! From tomorrow on, do not go after the calves.</l>
<l rend="indent">Stay here and make [yourself] beautiful.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
